+ *
+ * Drives the Samsung HDPTX PHY for HDMI TMDS output on RK3576/RK3588. The PHY
+ * is a UCLASS_PHY: the DW-HDMI-QP bridge configures the link rate through
+ * generic_phy_configure() and brings the lanes up with generic_phy_power_on().
+ * A UCLASS_CLK child bound to the same OF node (matching #clock-cells = <0>)
+ * publishes the pixel clock the VOP reparents its DCLK onto (pll_hdmiphy0);
+ * setting that clock's rate runs the ROPLL common configuration.
+ *
+ * Only the TMDS path is implemented: the DisplayPort (LCPLL) and HDMI2.1 FRL
+ * legs of the vendor combo driver are intentionally absent.
+ */
