+ * @color_depth: deep-color (10bpc) flag; the v1 TMDS path leaves it clear.
+ * @rate: the PHY output rate in Hz, published by the clock child.
+ * @pll_locked: set once the ROPLL reports lock.
+ * @apb_reset: PHY APB reset.
+ * @cmn_reset: PHY common-block reset.
+ * @init_reset: PHY init reset.
+ * @lane_reset: PHY lane reset.
+ */
